                     <interp inst="t18460105-368-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>for feloniously uttering a forged acquittance and receipt for 3<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 15<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., well knowing it to be forged, with intent to defraud <persName id="t18460105-name-143" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18460105-name-143" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18460105-name-143" type="surname" value="SIMS"></interp>
