                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-368-18460105 t18460105-368-punishment-9"></join>Confined Two Years</rs>.</hi>—(<hi rend="italic">See Cowan, Mayor</hi>, 5<hi rend="italic">th Session, p.</hi> 649.)</p>
               <p>(There was another indictment against the prisoner.)</p>
